---

<PageLayout
  title="Portofolio Jasa Bore Pile Profesional | Hutama Bore Pile"
  description="Lihat portofolio proyek jasa bore pile Hutama Bore Pile untuk rumah, gudang, gedung, dan berbagai proyek konstruksi di Pulau Jawa."
  eagerReveal
>
  <Hero layout="centered" size="sm" class="isolate" showHeroHalo>
    <Badge slot="badge" variant="brand" pill>
      <Icon name="layers" size="sm" />
      Portofolio
    </Badge>
    <h1 slot="title">Dokumentasi Proyek Bore Pile</h1>
    <p slot="description">
      Hutama Bore Pile telah menangani berbagai pekerjaan jasa bore pile dan pondasi bangunan untuk kebutuhan rumah tinggal, ruko, gudang, gedung, pabrik, hingga proyek konstruksi lainnya di berbagai kota di Pulau Jawa.
    </p>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Proyek -->
  <section class="py-[var(--space-section-md)] bg-background-secondary border-t border-border">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 flex flex-col gap-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center" data-reveal>
        <Badge variant="brand" pill>Proyek Kami</Badge>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Proyek Jasa Bore Pile yang Telah Dikerjakan
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {projects.map((project, i) => (
          <Card variant="elevated" hover padding="none" class="group flex flex-col" data-reveal data-reveal-delay={String(i % 3)}>
            <div class="overflow-hidden bg-background-tertiary">
              <img
                src={project.image}
                alt={project.title}
                class="w-full object-contain transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
                loading="lazy"
                is:inline
              />
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col p-6">
              <div class="mb-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/20 to-brand-500/5 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-500 shrink-0">
                  <Icon name={project.icon} size="sm" />
                </div>
                <Badge variant="brand" pill class="text-xs">{project.status}</Badge>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-base font-bold text-foreground mb-2">{project.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-foreground-muted leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-1">{project.desc}</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-auto">
                <Badge variant="brand">{project.type}</Badge>
                <Badge variant="brand">{project.pondasi}</Badge>
                <Badge variant="brand">{project.location}</Badge>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dokumentasi Lapangan -->
  <section class="py-[var(--space-section-md)] bg-background border-t border-border">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 flex flex-col gap-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center" data-reveal>
        <Badge variant="brand" pill>Dokumentasi</Badge>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Pengerjaan Menggunakan Tenaga Berpengalaman
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-foreground-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Setiap proyek dikerjakan oleh tim yang berpengalaman di bidang pondasi bore pile dengan dukungan alat kerja yang memadai.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        {[
          { icon: 'drill', text: 'Proses pengeboran' },
          { icon: 'layers', text: 'Pemasangan tulangan' },
          { icon: 'droplets', text: 'Pengecoran beton' },
          { icon: 'check-circle', text: 'Quality control' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <Card hover data-reveal class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/20 to-brand-500/5 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-500 shrink-0">
              <Icon name={item.icon} size="sm" />
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">{item.text}</p>
          </Card>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Kenapa Klien Memilih Kami -->
  <section class="py-[var(--space-section-md)] bg-background-secondary border-t border-border">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 flex flex-col gap-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center" data-reveal>
        <Badge variant="brand" pill>Keunggulan</Badge>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Kenapa Banyak Klien Memilih Hutama Bore Pile?
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center" data-reveal>
        {[
          'Pengerjaan profesional',
          'Tenaga berpengalaman',
          'Harga kompetitif',
          'Support proyek kecil & besar',
          'Survey lokasi',
          'Konsultasi gratis',
          'Area layanan luas',
        ].map((item) => (
          <Badge variant="brand" pill>{item}</Badge>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative z-10 py-[var(--space-section-md)] bg-background border-t border-border">
    <ImageCtaBand
      backgroundImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1756388812709-3d524bc42b9b?w=1920&h=800&fit=crop&q=80&auto=format"
      imageAlt="Pekerja konstruksi dan excavator di lokasi proyek bangunan"
    >
      <Badge variant="brand" pill class="mb-6">Konsultasi Gratis</Badge>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4 text-balance">
        Konsultasikan Proyek Anda Sekarang
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-foreground-muted mb-8 text-balance">
        Butuh jasa bore pile untuk rumah, gudang, ruko, gedung, atau proyek lainnya? Hubungi tim kami sekarang.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <Button size="lg" href={waLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hero-btn-brand">
          <Icon name="message-circle" size="sm" />
          WhatsApp: 0813-2804-803
        </Button>
        <Button size="lg" variant="outline" href="/contact">
          Kirim Pesan
          <Icon name="arrow-right" size="sm" />
        </Button>
      </div>
    </ImageCtaBand>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
